snippet.title: Math Blaster Mystery: The Great Brain Robbery Full Walkthrough
snippet.description:
Math Blaster Mystery: The Great Brain Robbery Full Walkthrough

Math Blaster Mystery: The Great Brain Robbery is a game created by Davidson Associates Inc. in 1994. In this game, you must help Rave return Big Brain's brain back from the evil Dr. Dabble.

Happy Halloween Everybody!
